    <h3>Estranged: The Departure (2020)</h3>
    <p>Follows the story of a fisherman, stranded on a mysterious island during a violent storm. Little does he know his adventure has just begun, and the island is home to more than it first seems.</p>
    <p><iframe style="max-width:100%" width="960" height="540" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/J7UFEdpQyf4" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
    <p>A game built with Unreal Engine 4, continuing the events of Act I. Released into Steam Early Access March 2017 with bi-weekly content updates for Windows and Linux until its release in 2020.</p>
    <p>Available on <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/582890">Steam for Windows, macOS, and Linux</a>, and on <a href="https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/estranged-the-departure-switch/">Nintendo eShop for Nintendo Switch</a></p>

    <h3>Estrangd: Act I (2014)</h3>
    <p>Tells the story of a lone fisherman, whose ship is stranded on a mysterious island during a violent storm. Explore the rich environments and meet the curious inhabitants of the island as you find a way back to the mainland.</p>
    <p><iframe style="max-width:100%" width="960" height="540" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/m240VFd9jxM" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
    <p>A free Source Engine game released on Steam in January 2014, with over 300,000 downloads and just under 6,000 reviews to date. It follows the story of a lone fisherman, stranded on an island during a violent storm. And zombies!</p>
    <p>Available on <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/261820">Steam for Windows and Linux</a></p>

